OL,3,C'Despicable' carer suffocated 90-year-
OL,4,Cold and stole #60 from her purse
OL,6,FA carer has been jailed for life for
OL,7,Fthe murder of a 90-year-old woman in
OL,8,Fher own home in "the ultimate breach
OL,9,Fof trust" - after she was caught on
OL,10,Fcamera stealing from her.
OL,12,FJane Hill, 52, hit Myra Thompson over
OL,13,Fthe head as she lay in bed before
OL,14,Ftaking a pillow and suffocating her as
OL,15,Fshe tried to fight back at her home in
OL,16,FSpital, on the Wirral, in April 2024.
