OL,6,FJailing Hill, who was one of Mrs
OL,7,FThompson's carers, for 22-and-a-half
OL,8,Fyears Recorder of Liverpool, Andrew
OL,9,FMenary KC, said the offence had been a
OL,10,F"gross breach of trust against a
OL,11,Fvulnerable woman".
OL,13,FJudge Menary said: "This was a cruel
OL,14,Fand callous offence involving
OL,15,Fsignificant planning and premeditation
OL,16,Fcommitted in gross breach of trust
OL,17,Fagainst a vulnerable woman in her own
OL,18,Fhome.
