OL,6,F"Her suffering during the time you
OL,7,Fwere attacking her must have been
OL,8,Fprofound."
OL,10,FLiverpool Crown Court heard a covert
OL,11,Fcamera was set up in the home of Mrs
OL,12,FThompson in Spital, Wirral, after she
OL,13,Ftold neighbours she suspected one of
OL,14,Fher carers was taking cash from her
OL,15,Fpurse, Liverpool Crown Court heard.
OL,17,FHill was seen stealing money from Mrs
OL,18,FThompson, on 12 April, and the agency
OL,19,Fworker was subsequently suspended by
OL,20,Fher employers after she "flatly"
OL,21,Fdenied the offence.
