OL,4,Cold and stole #60 from her purse
OL,6,F"You hit her several times over the
OL,7,Fhead with a metal flask and then
OL,8,Fapplied a pillow over her face so that
OL,9,Fshe was fatally suffocated.
OL,11,F"She had other injuries indicating she
OL,12,Ffought as strongly as she properly
OL,13,Fcould.
OL,15,F"You hoped her death would somehow
OL,16,Fenable you to keep your job and more
OL,17,Fsignificantly I'm sure you feared the
OL,18,Fmatter might go further and involve a
OL,19,Fcomplaint to the police.
