OL,6,F"You wanted to try to conceal the fact
OL,7,Fthat a crime had been committed by
OL,8,Fremoving the only person you thought
OL,9,Fwas a witness.
OL,11,F"This was therefore a premeditated
OL,12,Fmurder intended to obstruct the course
OL,13,Fof justice."
OL,15,FHill also admitted the theft of #60
OL,16,Fcash from Ms Thompson's purse on 12
OL,17,FApril.
