OL,6,FDetective Inspector Dave Jones, from
OL,7,FMerseyside Police, said it was a
OL,8,F"shocking and despicable" that Hill
OL,9,Fchose to carry out the attack on a
OL,10,Ffrail and elderly woman who should
OL,11,Fhave been safe in bed in her own home.
OL,13,F"She has shown no remorse over the
OL,14,Fdeath of Myra but will now spend a
OL,15,Fconsiderable period of time behind
OL,16,Fbars to think about her actions on
OL,17,Fthat night," DI Jones said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
