OL,6,FMyra's friend and neighbour Ann Jarvis
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement released by
OL,8,FMerseyside Police: "I have lost all
OL,9,Fconfidence and trust in the world and
OL,10,Fhumanity itself, as I try to
OL,11,Fcomprehend the brutal murder of my
OL,12,Fdear friend and neighbour Myra.
OL,14,F"Myra was like a sister to me and I
OL,15,Fkeep replaying over and over this day,
OL,16,Fand the shock of hearing of her
OL,17,Fkilling.
OL,26,@pD@TOUvD@AOU
