OL,6,FMyra's niece Anne Charters added: "As
OL,7,Fa family we are greatly relieved that
OL,8,Fthe murder investigation into Myra's
OL,9,Fdeath has finally come to an end,
OL,10,Fresulting in a fitting sentence for
OL,11,Fthe accused.
OL,13,F"To abuse a position of trust on
OL,14,Fsomeone as frail and vulnerable as my
OL,15,Faunty Myra and to then confront her
OL,16,Fwith such violence is something that
OL,17,Fhas been incredibly upsetting and
OL,18,Fdifficult to come to terms with.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
