OL,3,C'Despicable' carer suffocated 90-year-
OL,4,Cold and stole #60 from her purse
OL,6,F"We can only imagine the terror she
OL,7,Fexperienced during her final moments
OL,8,Fon the evening of 23 April in her own
OL,9,Fhome, a place where she was supposed
OL,10,Fto be safe.
OL,12,F"We are hoping that now justice has
OL,13,Fbeen served we can all move on and
OL,14,Fhope it will go some way towards
OL,15,Fhelping everyone directly affected by
OL,16,Fthis shocking case, to find some form
OL,17,Fof closure from what has ultimately
OL,18,Fbeen a living nightmare."
